\cf0 \ul \ulc0 You see this error message: qemu: could not load PC BIOS 'bios.bin'\ulnone \
Try adding the -L option with the path to the pc-bios folder like this: -L <path>/pc-bios\
\
\ul HELP! I'm stuck in full screen mode and don't remember how to get out!\ulnone \
Try to shut down your operating system. That will cause QEMU to quit.\
\
\ul This emulator is too slow\ulnone \
Emulation is an extra layer that has to run on top of the host computer's CPU. The more layers in between your program and your CPU, the slower your program will probably be. Having the latest and greatest in computer technology helps.\
